'''Saffa paintings''' were an important form of artistic development in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. Produced by the [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Saffa (species)|Saffa]] [[Species/Legends|species]] after their contact with the [[Thennqora]], this type of artwork reached its height approximately [[2200 BBY/Legends|2200]] to [[1569 BBY]].

